item.description: This volleyball event will be outdoors on a grass field. At least one net will be doubles, intended for A/AA players, and possibly reverse coed depending on the attendees. The other net will be either doubles or, 4's depending on the number of attendees. It may be reverse coed depending on the attendees. Please note in your RSVP if you have a preference for playing doubles or 4's.
item.name: Advanced Outdoor (Grass) Volleyball
